UID:MdNecZI5hyytB5JCggWQt
SUMMARY:Catbird Opening First Seattle Store at University Village
DTSTAMP:20260326T121338Z
DTSTART:20260402T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Catbird\, the Brooklyn-based demi-fine jewelry brand\, is excit
	ed to announce it will be opening its first storefront at University Villa
	ge in Seattle on Thursday\, 4/2! Join us to celebrate Catbird’s latest ope
	ning with a number of in-store treats and activations including wine\, min
	i floral bouquets and more! The new store will feature cases lined with Ca
	tbird’s timeless 14k gold and sterling silver classics\, alongside Forever
	 Bracelets\, a build-your-own-charm counter\, and more for shoppers to cus
	tomize! \n\nStarting opening day \\(4/2\\) and running through Sunday\, 4/
	5\, in-store activations will include: \n\nOpening Day \\(Thursday\, 4/2\\
	): All weekend long\, the first 100 guests daily will receive limited edit
	ion Catbird tote bags & the Toy Bow charm only ever available at store ope
	nings – complimentary with any purchase $350\\+. The first 15 customers in
	 line on Thursday will receive a complimentary $50 gift card. \n\nOpening 
	Weekend \\(Friday\, 4/3-Sunday\, 4/5\\): The first 15 customers in line on
	 Friday will also receive a complimentary $50 gift card. On Saturday and S
	unday\, guests can enjoy special treats\, including wine\, pastries\, and 
	mini bouquets\, with purchase. \n\nOpening Day & Weekend\n\nDate: 4/2-4/5\
	n\nTime: Thursday-Saturday: 11am - 7pm\n\nLocation: 2326 Northeast Univers
	ity Village Street\, Suite 7\, Seattle\, WA 98105\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amc
	ity.com/events/#/details/catbird-opening-first-seattle-store-at-university
	-village/18385008/2026-04-02T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/catbird-opening-first-sea
	ttle-store-at-university-village/18385008/2026-04-02T00
LOCATION:Catbird\, 2326 Northeast University Village Street\, Suite 7\, Sea
	ttle\, WA
